column2: # We descriminate between important and less important variables based on their discriminatory power (based on the distance between means of their corresponding distribution).
# p-value>0.05, we accept null hypotehsis: true difference in means is equal to 0.#no significant mean difference
filter(df, TIPO == "Bajo riesgo")$Ratio_Endeudamiento and filter(df, TIPO == "Riesgo medio")$Ratio_Endeudamiento
t.test(filter(df, TIPO == "Riesgo medio")$Ratio_Endeudamiento,filter(df, TIPO == "Alto riesgo")$Ratio_Endeudamiento)#no significant mean difference
filter(df, TIPO == "Riesgo medio")$Ratio_Endeudamiento and filter(df, TIPO == "Alto riesgo")$Ratio_Endeudamiento
filter(df, TIPO == "Bajo riesgo")$Ratio_Endeudamiento and filter(df, TIPO == "Alto riesgo")$Ratio_Endeudamiento
